  fhir:description [ fhir:v "This document describes Sensotrend's implementation of the [HL7 FHIR IPS](https://hl7.org/fhir/uv/ips/) format of the [International Patient Summary (IPS)](https://international-patient-summary.net/) specification both as a client app and as a FHIR server. It also includes and extensive example patient summary for Mikael, an example patient."] ; # 
